<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome to Flyobo Travel</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 32px; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7fa, #ffffff); color: #333;">

  <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); overflow: hidden;">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4B0082, #00b4d8); padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #fff; font-size: 28px;">
        Welcome to <span style="color: #FFD700;">Flyobo Travel</span>
      </h1>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 16px; color: #e0f7ff;">
        "Jobs fill your pocket, but adventures fill your soul." – Jaime Lyn Beatty
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div style="padding: 36px 30px;">
      <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We're absolutely thrilled to welcome you to <strong>Flyobo Travel</strong> — your gateway to extraordinary adventures and unforgettable experiences! 🌍✈️
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Here's what's waiting for you as a member:
      </p>

      <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #444;">
        <li>✅ Access to exclusive travel packages and deals</li>
        <li>✅ Personalized travel recommendations</li>
        <li>✅ Real-time booking and trip management</li>
        <li>✅ 24/7 customer support and travel assistance</li>
        <li>✅ Member-only discounts and special offers</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Quote Box -->
      <div style="margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background: #f9fbff; border-left: 5px solid #4B0082; font-style: italic; color: #555;">
        "Not all those who wander are lost." – J.R.R. Tolkien
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Button -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="https://flyobo.com" style="background: #4B0082; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(75, 0, 130, 0.3); display: inline-block;">
          Explore Your Dashboard
        </a>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8;">
        Let's turn dreams into destinations and transform miles into moments. Your next adventure awaits!
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 36px; font-size: 16px;">
        With wanderlust and excitement,<br />
        <strong>The Flyobo Travel Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div style="background: #f1f1f1; text-align: center; padding: 20px 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #777;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Flyobo Travel. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 5px;">"Flyobo: Fly Off, Break Out"</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
